               <msContents>
                  <summary>
                     Second of an incomplete set of six volumes of the <title>Rawz̤at al-Ṣafā</title> (Garden of Purity), a general history from the creation of the world to the time of the author, together
                     with <ref target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/manuscript_6656"
                     ><idno>Persian MS 173</idno></ref>, <ref
                        target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/manuscript_14610">175</ref>, <ref
                           target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/manuscript_6657">176</ref>, 
                  <ref target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/manuscript_6658">177</ref>, and <ref
                     target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/manuscript_6658">178</ref>, but it lacks the fourth volume and a geographical appendix often added as the eighth. 
                  While nearly uniformly bound, the different formats and colophons within the set indicate completion in different location and times.</summary>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="manuscript_14609-item1">
                     <author key="person_175393012" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/175393012/" change="#ids-cleanup">
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">Mīr Khvānd, Muḥammad ibn Khāvandshāh, 1433-1498</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa">مير خواند، محمد بن خواندشاه</persName>
                     </author>
                     <editor role="scr"><persName type="standard">Ḥusayn ibn Hasan</persName></editor>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_273" change="#ids-cleanup">Rawz̤at al-Ṣafā fī Sīrat al-Anbiyā wa-al-Mulūk</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="alt" key="work_273">Rawz̤at al-Ṣafā</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_273" change="#ids-cleanup">روضة الصفاء فی سیرة الانبيا و الملوك</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar" type="basmallah"><locus from="1b" to="1b"> برگ ۱پ (folio 1b):</locus>
                        عنوان صحیفهٔ مرادات و فهرست مجموعهٔ سعادت مبین..‌. </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="fa">
                        <locus from="520b" to="520b"> برگ ۵۲۰پ (folio 520b):
                        </locus> علی مالیاء قدیر و بالرجبات حدیر و السلام علی خمسه ابیع اللهی (؟). </explicit>
                     <colophon xml:lang="fa">
                        <locus from="520b" to="520b"> برگ ۵۲۰پ (folio 520b):</locus>
                        تمام شد دفتر دویم کتاب روضة الصفا بعون حق عز و علا بتاریخ سیوم شهر ذی القعده فی یوم الاحد بخط اضعاف العباد حسین این حسن...  
                     </colophon>
                     <colophon>Signed by the scribe <persName type="standard" role="scr" key="">Ḥusayn ibn Hasan</persName>; however, he only indicates that he completed it on <q xml:lang="en">Sunday, 3 Ẕī-l-Ḥijjah</q> but omits the year.</colophon>
                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>
                  </msItem>
